oposta.</p></div><div class=\"\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(30px);transition:opacity 0.6s cubic-bezier(0.44,0,0.56,1) 0s, transform 0.6s cubic-bezier(0.44,0,0.56,1) 0s;will-change:opacity, transform\"><div class=\"rounded-[30px] border border-white/10 bg-[#0c0d10] p-3 sm:p-4 md:p-5\"><div class=\"grid lg:grid-cols-[1fr_minmax(0,440px)] gap-3 sm:gap-4\"><div class=\"rounded-[22px] bg-bg-card/40 p-6 sm:p-8 flex flex-col\"><p class=\"text-[11px] uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-dark mb-7\">Incluído em todos os pacotes</p><div class=\"grid sm:grid-cols-2 gap-x-6 gap-y-7\"><div class=\"flex gap-3.5\"><span class=\"grid place-items-center w-9 h-9 shrink-0 rounded-lg border border-white/10 bg-white/[0.04] text-accent\"><svg width=\"17\" height=\"17\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"><path d=\"m15 5 4 4\"></path><path d=\"M3 21v-3L14 7l3 3L6 21H3Z\"></path></svg></span><div class=\"min-w-0\"><h3 class=\"text-white font-heading text-[15px] font-medium leading-tight\">Design à medida</h3><p class=\"mt-1 text-muted text-[13px] leading-snug\">Nada de templates. Um site feito de raiz, com a identidade do teu negócio.</p></div></div><div class=\"flex gap-3.5\"><span class=\"grid place-items-center w-9 h-9 shrink-0 rounded-lg border border-white/10 bg-white/[0.04] text-accent\"><svg width=\"17\" height=\"17\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"><path d=\"M13 2 3 14h7l-1 8 10-12h-7l1-8Z\"></path></svg></span><div class=\"min-w-0\"><h3 class=\"text-white font-heading text-[15px] font-medium leading-tight\">Ultra-rápido</h3><p class=\"mt-1 text-muted text-[13px] leading-snug\">PageSpeed 95+. Sites lentos perdem clientes; o teu carrega num instante.</p></div></div><div class=\"flex gap-3.5\"><span class=\"grid place-items-center w-9 h-9 shrink-0 rounded-lg border border-white/10 bg-whit