em templates</li><li class=\"flex items-start gap-2.5 text-sm text-white/85\"><span class=\"grid place-items-center w-5 h-5 shrink-0 mt-px rounded-full bg-accent/15 text-accent\"><svg width=\"12\" height=\"12\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"\"><path d=\"M20 6 9 17l-5-5\"></path></svg></span>SEO técnico incluído</li><li class=\"flex items-start gap-2.5 text-sm text-white/85\"><span class=\"grid place-items-center w-5 h-5 shrink-0 mt-px rounded-full bg-accent/15 text-accent\"><svg width=\"12\" height=\"12\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"\"><path d=\"M20 6 9 17l-5-5\"></path></svg></span>Domínio + alojamento tratados</li></ul></div><div class=\"mt-7\"><p class=\"text-[11px] uppercase tracking-[0.16em] text-dark mb-3\">Escolhe o pacote</p><div class=\"flex flex-wrap gap-2\"><button type=\"button\" aria-pressed=\"false\" class=\"rounded-full border px-3.5 py-2 sm:py-1.5 text-[12px] font-medium transition-colors cursor-pointer border-white/10 bg-white/[0.03] text-muted hover:text-white hover:border-white/25\">Landing Page</button><button type=\"button\" aria-pressed=\"true\" class=\"rounded-full border px-3.5 py-2 sm:py-1.5 text-[12px] font-medium transition-colors cursor-pointer border-accent/50 bg-accent/15 text-white\">Website Essencial</button><button type=\"button\" aria-pressed=\"false\" class=\"rounded-full border px-3.5 py-2 sm:py-1.5 text-[12px] font-medium transition-colors cursor-pointer border-white/10 bg-white/[0.03] text-muted hover:text-white hover:border-white/25\">Website Profissional</button><button type=\"button\" aria-pressed=\"false\" class=\"rounded-full border px-3.5 py-2 sm:py-1.5 text-[12px] font-medium transition-colors cursor-pointer border-white/10 bg-white/[0.03] text-muted hover:text-white hover:border-white/25\">Redesign de Site</button><button type=\"button\" aria-pressed=\"false\" class=\"rounded-full border px-3.5 py-2 sm:py-1.5 text-[12px] font-medium transition-colors cursor-pointer border-white/10 bg-white/[0.03] text-muted hover:text-white hover:border-white/25\">Loja Online</button></div></div><div class=\"mt-7\"><a class=\"nova-btn font-body w-full\" href=\"/contacto?servico=Websites%20%26%20Lojas%20Online\"><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"nova-btn__glow\"></span><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"nova-btn__ring\"></span><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"nova-btn__shine\"></span><span class=\"nova-btn__label\">Pedir orçamento grátis</span></a></div><p class=\"mt-4 flex items-center justify-center gap-2 text-[12px] text-muted\"><svg width=\"12\" height=\"12\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"text-accent\"><path d=\"M20 6 9 17l-5-5\"></path></svg>Orçamento e diagnóstico gratuitos</p></div></div></div></div></div></div></section><section class=\"bg-bg border-t border-white/10 py-24 px-6\" aria-labelledby=\"faq\"><script type=\"application/ld+json\">{\"@context\":\"https://schema.org\",\"@type\":\"FAQPage\",\"mainEntity\":[{\"@type\":\"Question\",\"name\":\"Quanto tempo demora a ter o site pronto?\",\"acceptedAnswer\":{\"@type\":\"Answer\",\"text\":\"Depende da dimensão: um site institucional fica normalmente pronto mais depressa do que uma loja online. Indico um prazo concreto na proposta — e cumpro-o.\"}},{\"@type\":\"Question\",\"name\":\"O site fica meu?\",\"acceptedAnswer\":{\"@type\":\"Answer\",\"text\":\"Sim. O site e o domínio são teus, no teu nome, sem ficares preso a mim.\"}},{\"@type\":\"Question\",\"name\":\"E a manutenção e o alojamento?\",\"acceptedAnswer\":{\"@type\":\"Answer\",\"text\":\"Trato do domínio e do alojamento por ti e deixo o site a funcionar. Para evoluções contínuas (alterações, SEO, conteúdo) há planos mensais — mas sem obrigação.\"}},{\"@type\":\"Question\",\"name\":\"Tenho de escrever os textos?\",\"acceptedAnswer\":{\"@type\":\"Answer\",\"text\":\"Não precisas. Ajudo-te com os textos e o conteúdo, escritos para SEO e para converter — só validas.\"}},{\"@type\":\"Question\",\"name\":\"Já tenho um site. Aproveitas ou fazes de novo?\",\"acceptedAnswer\":{\"@type\":\"Answer\",\"text\":\"Depende do que tens. Posso fazer um redesign (a partir de 590€) ou criar um novo de raiz — digo-te com honestidade o que faz mais sentido para os teus objetivos e orçamento.\"}},{\"@type\":\"Question\",\"name\":\"Como começo?\",\"acceptedAnswer\":{\"@type\":\"Answer\",\"text\":\"Pedes um orçamento no formulário (2 minutos). Respondo em menos de 2 horas, sem compromisso.\"}}]}</script><div class=\"max-w-[820px] mx-auto\"><div class=\"text-center mb-12\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(30px);transition:opacity 0.6s cubic-bezier(0.44,0,0.56,1) 0s, transform 0.6s cubic-bezier(0.44,0,0.56,1) 0s;will-change:opacity, transform\"><p class=\"text-[11px] uppercase tracking-[0.22em] text-dark mb-4\">FAQ</p><h2 id=\"faq\" class=\"text-white\">Perguntas frequentes sobre websites</h2></div><div class=\"\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(30px);transition:opacity 0.6s cubic-bezier(0.44,0,0.56,1) 0s, transform 0.6s cubic-bezier(0.44,0,0.56,1) 0s;will-change:opacity, transform\"><div class=\"flex flex-col gap-3\"><div class=\"rounded-2xl border transition-colors duration-300\n              border-accent/30 bg-bg-card\"><h3><button id=\":R1acvfesq:-q-0\" aria-expanded=\"true\" aria-controls=\":R1acvfesq:-a-0\" class=\"w-full text-left px-6 py-5 flex items-center justify-between gap-4 focus-visible:outline focus-visible:outline-2 focus-visible:outline-accent rounded-2xl\"><span class=\"font-heading text-base md:text-lg transition-colors text-white\">Quanto tempo demora a ter o site pronto?</span><span class=\"relative w-4 h-4 shrink-0 text-accent\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"absolute top-1/2 left-0 w-4 h-0.5 -translate-y-1/2 r